Paper: hep-th/9201079

Date: 1992-01-31

Title: Fusion and singular vectors in A1{(1)} highest weight cyclic modules

Authors: M. Bauer and N. Sochen

Comments: 42 pages

Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 152 (1993) 127-160

We show how the interplay between the fusion formalism of conformal fieldtheory and the Knizhnik--Zamolodchikov equation leads to explicit formulae forthe singular vectors in the highest weight representations of A1{(1)}.